Description:
A piece of haven on 870m2 approx
Perfectly positioned in a quiet court sits this amazing opportunity that you will not want to pass up.
Boasting a fantastic family friendly floor plan with a centrally located kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and adjoining family/meals area, two additional living area and five bedrooms including a great size master with walk in robe and ensuite while the remaining bedrooms have built in robes.
Step outside through sliding doors to the fantastic outdoor undercover entertaining area with your own spa and generously sized backyard.
Adding to the fantastic layout is a central family bathroom, separate laundry and double car garage with internal access.
Other features include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ceiling fans, extra split system, 20 solar panels and extra off street parking.
With all these great features this home won't wait around for long. Don't miss this opportunity. Call now to organise an inspection.

Potential Plus!
This two bedroom unit is a great property for down sizes as well as for astute investors. Overall this property has great potential for someone who is downsizing or wishes to get their foot in the door of the ever competitive Cranbourne property market.

Description:
Fantastic Family Home in a Top Location with Multiple Living Areas!
If you are on the hunt for an exceptional home that offers an easier, more luxurious lifestyle, then don't settle for anything less than perfect. When it comes to comfort, space and decadent entertaining opportunities, this classic family home with delightful street appeal leaves nothing to be desired.
With 4 large bedrooms on offer, master with walk in robe and full ensuite whilst the remaining 3 bedrooms are all equipped with double built in robes and conveniently centred around the main bathroom which enjoys solar hot water. The heart of this home features a spacious fully-equipped kitchen providing great bench space, abundance of cupboards and quality appliances. Boasting 3 impressive separate living zones offering ducted heating for all year round comfort, this home provides the perfect place to relax and unwind with enough room for the whole family.
Those who like to entertain will be simply delighted by the huge covered alfresco area ideal for BBQs on a summers evening with family and friends, which overlooks the peaceful and private rear yard with plenty of room for those with kids and pets. With a double garage and large driveway, parking will not be a problem.
Set on a spacious 571m2 block and located in the exclusive Brookland Green Estate, with easy access to all amenities and main roads while being surrounded by parks, nature trails and the wonderful Royal Botanic Gardens this home is worth a look!

Description:
4000m2 of Pure Serenity!
Surrounded by beautiful homes in the much sought after and rarely offered Earlston Circuit, is this stunning quality family home. Combine this with an acre of land, you have a lifestyle that offers space, seclusion and absolute bliss.
With a well designed layout the 3 separate living areas include a formal lounge and dining room with a built in bar. The family room adjoining the large timber kitchen opens out onto a massive paved outdoor pergola while the separate rumpus room features a log fire and beautiful glass atrium.
Other features include;
*Master Bedroom with WIR and Ensuite
*Additional Bedrooms with double BIR
*Ducted Heating, Evaporative and Split System Cooling
*Security Alarm & Ducted Vacuum System
*Fernery with a Family Size Spa
*3 Car Brick Garage (20' x 30' )
*3 Stables and a 27,000 litre Water Tank
*Rumpus Room with a Private Entrance
On 4197m2 of land there is ample room for a pony, alpacas or a market garden. Maybe put in a swimming pool or a tennis court. The opportunities on offer are simply endless.
Just 4 minutes from Cranbourne CBD and within close proximity to schools, sporting facilities, all major freeways and public transport, 1 acre properties like this are as rare as hen’s teeth.
Don’t be the one to say ‘we should have bought it’ Be the one that Did!

Description:
**GRAND OPENING THIS SATURDAY AT 1:20PM** A TOTAL TRANSFORMATION THATS A REAL SURPRISE - THE PERFECT ENTERTAINER!
RANGEBANK ESTATE: Approaching this home from the street you take in its well-maintained gardens and individual brick facade, but it doesnt quite prepare you for what you find behind the front door. Step inside to find a home that has been totally rejuvenated with style and function at the forefront.
Light, spacious and impeccably finished the new carpets, neutral paint tones and designer level presentation give it a real edge that will simply appeal to anyone and everyone. The open concept living space incorporates the lounge, dining and family areas all flanking the renovated galley style kitchen with stainless steel appliances.
There are 3 robed bedrooms as well as a 4th bedroom/home office plus 2 renovated bathrooms including a full ensuite running off the master retreat. 2 split system heater/air conditioners keep the temperature just right, whilst outside you will find ample car accommodation between the main double garage and the additional side garage that is perfect for tradies or those with recreational vehicles!
The backyard is a perfect spot to relax, play and entertain with a vast paved area and extensive decking set under the huge pergola. Don't forget the 2 garden sheds that provide additional storage space!
If you believe in the age old theory that a top location equals great real estate then this is an absolute must to inspect! Sensational position within walking distance to Rangebank Primary School and Kindergarten with Lawson Pool Recreation Reserve literally down the road. Close proximity to buses, Merinda Park train station and Thompson Road, which provides direct access to all of the shopping facilities on offer at the Cranbourne Home Maker Centre!
With turnover in this popular estate at an all-time low don't muck around or else you will miss out!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW (PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS)!

Description:
COSY, CUTE AND NEAT AS A PIN! COME ON IN!
CRANBOURNE - With plenty of room to move and room for further improvement, this established home is sure to inspire the renovator in you or give you options to create that special place to call home. As an astute investor, developer or first home buyer, you will love the open plan living, well appointed kitchen space with dishwasher, 4 good size bedrooms, 3 with built in robes and updated laundry and bathroom with spa bath. We can't forget the fully self contained one bedroom Granny Flat in the backyard either! You could create something really special here as the current family have done for the past six years. This cosy home has a fabulous outdoor, undercover entertainment space, two great size garden sheds and a fully fenced backyard to love and enjoy with the family. A good old fashioned game of backyard cricket or bocce, bbq with friends or room to create something else that takes your imagination. This lovely home will be popular with both handy first home buyers and those looking to add to their investment portfolio, and is just waiting for you to bring your sketchpad and your imagination! It's a blank canvas and the opportunities are endless. There is also real potential for subdivision (STCA). The property is located within walking distance to the neighbourhood shops, Cranbourne railway station and only a short drive to all that this growing suburb has to offer including a choice of local primary and secondary schools, shopping centres, Cranbourne Homemaker Centre, medical centres and sporting venues.
Cranbourne Central
The central area of Cranbourne is one of the most established and sought after areas. With a mix of older homes on larger blocks and units. Located within walking distance to all facilities, including the newly renovated Cranbourne Park, a range of restaurants, Cranbourne Secondary College and Cranbourne Train Station. Cranbourne Central provides the perfect combination for any resident.

Description:
PRETTY AS A PICTURE AND PERFECTLY POSITIONED....
CRANBOURNE CENTRAL - All the hard work has been done but there's still room to add your own touch if you want to! Would you like a property that ticks all the boxes? Are you an investor, renovator or are you just looking for your next home where you can sit down and relax? Well, it is all here at 7 Clairmont Avenue Cranbourne. A true gem of a home conveniently located within walking distance to Cranbourne railway station and all that this growing suburb has to offer including shopping centres, local schools, medical centres and sporting venues. Welcome to your new home or investment opportunity! You'll be surprised at the overall condition of this lovely established 4 bedroom or 3 plus study home, sitting on a 639 sqm block, built in 1974 from quality sandstone rough cut bricks, with a colorbond roof and modest improvements over the years have made for comfortable living; this home oozes character, charm and warmth. Home is where the heart is and the heart has been involved in the making of the gorgeous low maintenance landscaped gardens surrounded by bluestone edging, complete with undercover alfresco bbq area and a huge fully plumbed garage/workshop perfect for the home handyperson and an extra garden shed/workshop or storage shed. Plenty of car parking space too. Great for the first home buyer, or anyone looking for an affordable entry level opportunity into the property market in this most sought after central location. Comprising 4 robed bedrooms or 3 plus study, renovated family bathroom with two separate toilets, open plan kitchen/meals, separate laundry, formal lounge with ceiling fan, split system heating/cooling and the added coziness of Coonara wood fired heating for those chilly cooler months. A charming and cosy home and your own private oasis awaits! This gorgeous home is in a fabulous location and close to all local amenities. It doesn't get any better than this! Make me an offer my Vendor can't refuse!
CRANBOURNE CENTRAL
The central area of Cranbourne is one of the most established and sought after areas. With a mix of older homes on larger blocks and units. Located within walking distance to all facilities, including the newly renovated Cranbourne Park, a range of restaurants, Cranbourne Secondary College and Cranbourne Train Station. Cranbourne Central provides the perfect combination for any resident.

* Renovated family bathroom
* Renovated toilet

* Short drive to Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre

Description:
This is The One
Immaculately presented with high quality finishes that are second to none, is this 30 plus squares Henley built home offering a functional free-flowing floor plan and modern aspects throughout. From the moment you enter this stunning home you will be thoroughly impressed with complete separate grand master bedroom inclusive of a large walk in robe and ensuite complete with double basins. Other three large bedrooms offer double built in robes and are in close proximity to the family bathroom.
The spectacular kitchen of the home is no less impressive with stone benchtops, European style stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and an oversized pantry. All this and a whole lot more overlooking a huge open plan family/meals area with lots of natural light flowing into the house. In addition to living and dining this
beautiful large home offers formal lounge, rear rumpus and kids retreat area. Extras include; ducted heating, internal access from double garage, quality fittings, high output led downlights...and the list goes on
Located in the very desirable young patch of Cranbourne, surrounded with quiet neighbourhood and great schools such as Cranbourne Carlisle primary school, moreover a short walk to Springhill shopping centre and easy access to Monash freeway entrance
Call Harry Brar today! This property will not last long!
